   100â†’class ReviewerLoader:
   101â†’    """
   102â†’    Loads the 5 fixed reviewer configurations from wfc/reviewers/.
   103â†’
   104â†’    Each reviewer directory contains:
   105â†’    - PROMPT.md (required) - The reviewer's system prompt
   106â†’    - KNOWLEDGE.md (optional) - Accumulated domain knowledge
